data.description: Don't miss this Summer Park Community Condo, it has it ALL! HOA includes water, basic TV, Clubhouse access, gym, pool, hot tub, billiard room, lawn fertilizer, lawn maintenance, snow removal, siding, and roof! Low home owners insurance since the roof and siding is covered by HOA!  3 finished floors in this condo! Turn the basement into a 3 bedroom suit! Wet bar in the basement, fridge and microwave set up, ready to GO! Tile floors in the kitchen, XL tall kitchen cabinets. Gas fireplace in the living room. Great separated floor plan. 2 car oversized garage! Covered front porch. Easy access visitor parking near by!
